{"tid":1614883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【修例風波】全綫車站今日可開放 港鐵強烈譴責破壞及暴力行為","createTime":"2019-10-03T02:23:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:30.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b03e814f58b245f17b91b5e24862d1f5d05f4c81","tid":1614883,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:23:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%85%A8%E7%B6%AB%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%AF%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E5%8F%8A%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-220900206.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B6%25AB%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%25AB%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%258F%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%25BC%25B7%25E7%2583%2588%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%25A3%259E%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258A%259B%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA-220900206.html&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7OgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=5aea9c55\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E5%85%A8%E7%B6%AB%E8%BB%8A%E7%AB%99%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E5%8F%AF%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE-%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%BC%B7%E7%83%88%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC%E7%A0%B4%E5%A3%9E%E5%8F%8A%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA-220900206.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/puIXl6zV.G96bplLdBNp6A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20191003a061041.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FpuIXl6zV.G96bplLdBNp6A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20191003a061041.jpg&h=285710d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港鐵全綫車站今日可開放。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】港鐵表示，今日全綫港鐵車站均可開放，為乘客提供服務。然而，由於個別車站被破壞，部分車站出入口或設施需要較長的復修時間，乘客於使用相關設施時或需要較長時間，並留意車站告示或職員指示。<br />\n<br />\n經初步點算後，昨晚至少有十多個車站的設施遭受嚴重破壞。受損設施主要包括出入閘機、售票機、閉路電視及玻璃圍欄等，部分車站牆身及地面亦被塗鴉。損毀較為嚴重的車站包括將軍澳綫調景嶺站、將軍澳站及坑口站，東鐵綫大圍站、沙田站及大學站。其他多個車站的設施亦有不同程度的損毀。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵公司會盡力復修以減低對乘客的影響﹐並再次強烈譴責有關破壞及暴力行為，公司已就有關案件報警。<br />\n<br />\n黃大仙站都頂唔順水浸鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜仲有服務緊市民咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359e03f27ed11cd9de0b195c1dcd4621493c7ec1","tid":1614883,"uid":260036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:25:03.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"b46c26e55be586636fe2664493b661cfd8bf9eec","tid":1614883,"uid":259813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T02:40:30.000Z","msg":"老實，譴責得多就唔值錢"}]}